                    <div class="p-4 bg-dark text-white">
                        <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark fw-bold px-3 py-2 mb-2 fs-6 text-uppercase">⚡ ORAS NA LANG!</span>
                        <h3 class="fw-extrabold mb-2">Flash Sale: Up to 30% OFF!</h3>
                        <p class="text-light small opacity-75 mb-3">Ayaw sipyata kini, Boss! Tanan nimong paborito nga produkto, dako kaayo og usos karong adlawa ra.</p>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-secondary px-3 py-2 rounded fw-bold text-warning" style="min-width: 60px;">2h</div>
                            <div class="bg-secondary px-3 py-2 rounded fw-bold text-warning" style="min-width: 60px;">45m</div>
                            <div class="bg-secondary px-3 py-2 rounded fw-bold text-warning" style="min-width: 60px;">12s</div>
                        </div>

                        <a href="/?sort=discount" class="btn btn-warning w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill text-dark">
                            Pahimusli ang Discount!
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-white border-top pt-5 pb-4 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row gy-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">B-HUB<span class="text-primary">.</span></h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small">Ang pinakabarato ug pinakapaspas nga online shop sa tibuok lungsod.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <a href="#" class="text-dark"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-dark"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="text-dark"><i class="bi bi-messenger"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-6 col-6">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3">Shop</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled small">
